Package: com.albrhi.tweak
Name: Albrhi for Instagram
Version: 3.0.24
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64
Description: The most complete Instagram experience for iOS — bilingual (العربية / English) with automatic RTL.
 .
 Downloads — save posts, reels, stories, carousels, DM media and HD profile pictures in their maximum available quality. Pick the resolution before saving, grab reel audio only, or strip audio from video. Media can be filed automatically into a dedicated Photos album.
 .
 Cleaner feed — remove ads, sponsored and suggested posts, suggested users and reels, Threads posts, Meta AI, the friends map, trending searches and the explore grid.
 .
 Privacy — view stories without a seen receipt, hide the typing indicator, keep deleted messages, disable screenshot detection and replay visual messages without limits.
 .
 Reels and feed control — tap-to-pause or tap-to-mute, always-on scrubber, no auto-unmute, anti doom-scrolling limits and disabled video autoplay.
 .
 Confirmations — an optional prompt before liking, following, calling, reposting, commenting or sending a voice message, so a mis-tap never becomes a notification.
 .
 Native design — settings built with UIKit inset-grouped lists, SF Symbols, a customizable accent color and full dark-mode support. Open the panel by holding the menu button on your profile, or the home tab.
 .
 Developed by Ibrahim Ismail AL-Rahn. Albrhi is an educational and corrective derivative of SCInsta by SoCuul, rebuilt with AI assistance to improve code quality, design, performance and user experience. Free and open source under the GNU GPL v3 — original authorship fully credited and preserved.
Homepage: https://github.com/ibrahim2100/instv3
Maintainer: Ibrahim Ismail AL-Rahn <ibrahimalrahan01@gmail.com>
Author: Ibrahim Ismail AL-Rahn (based on SCInsta by SoCuul, GPLv3)
Section: Tweaks
Depends: mobilesubstrate
Tag: role::enduser
